<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Indian Cuisines</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #fafafa;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        p.intro {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        nav {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b03a2e;
        }

        section {
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        section h2 {
            padding: 10px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        section figure {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section figcaption {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        /* 🎨 Color-coded headers */
        .bengali h2 {
            background-color: #e67e22;
        }

        .gujarati h2 {
            background-color: #27ae60;
        }

        .mughlai h2 {
            background-color: #8e44ad;
        }

        .punjabi h2 {
            background-color: #d4ac0d;
        }

        .southindian h2 {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
    <!DOCTYPE html>
    <html>
    
    <head>
        <title>Text on Image</title>
        <style>
            .image-container {
                position: relative;
                display: inline-block;
                width: 600px;
                /*image size */
            }
    
            .image-container img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
    
            .image-text {
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 0;
                /* stick to bottom */
                left: 0;
                width: 100%;
                /* span full width */
                background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
                /* dark overlay bar */
                color: white;
                font-size: 1.2em;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: center;
                border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
                /* match rounded corners */
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    
    <body>
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="spice.jpg" alt="Indian Spices">
            <div class="image-text">The traditional food of India has been widely appreciated for its fabulous use of herbs and
            spices. Indian cuisine is known for its large assortment dishes. The cooking style varies from region to
            region and is largely divided into South Indian & North Indian cuisine. India is quite famous for its
            diverse multi cuisine available in a large number of restaurants and hotel resorts, which is reminiscent of
            unity in diversity.</div>
        </div>
    </body>
    
    </html>

<style>
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 20px;
        background-color: rgb(77, 255, 0);
        text-align: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .box {
        background-color: rgb(254, 114, 0);
        width: 100px;
        height: 80px;
        line-height: 100px;
        border: 2px solid red;
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="box">Bengali</div>
        <div class="box">Gujarati</div>
        <div class="box">Mughlai</div>
        <div class="box">South indian</div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

